'''''Centropogon chiltasonensis''''' is a species of [[plant]] in the [[Campanulaceae]] family. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Ecuador]]. [[Category:Flora of Ecuador]] Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist [[montane]]s. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]]. 

